project_descr: Indonesia is among the pioneer countries in the Asia Pacific region to establish the institutional governance for the MDGs and the SDGs at national and local levels, in the form of presidential regulations and the MDGs and SDGs secretariats.

outputs.output_descr: SDGs related policy, advocacy and institution developed and/or strengthened. Hence, it is important for Indonesia to mainstream SDGs into national and subnational development planning and action plans;
